ead F.C.|Peterhead]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===Major Honours===\n[[Lowland Football League|Lowland League]] play-off<ref name=prom18/>\n* '''Winners''': [[2017\u201318 Lowland Football League#Lowland League play-off|2017\u201318]]\n\n[[East of Scotland Football League]]<ref name=\"hons\">{{cite web|title=Honours|url=http://www.keltyhearts.co.uk/club-history/4584810886|website=Kelty Hearts FC|accessdate=20 May 2018}}</ref>\n*'''Winners''': [[2017\u201318 East of Scotland Football League|2017\u201318]]\n\nKing Cup\n* '''Winners''': 2017\u201318\n\n[[Scottish Junior Football East Region Super League|East Region Super League]]<ref name=\"hons\" />\n*'''Winners''': [[2014\u201315 East Superleague|2014\u201315]], [[2016\u201317 East Superleague|2016\u201317]]\n*Runners-up: [[2015\u201316 East Superleague|2015\u201316]]\n\n[[Scottish Junior Cup]]<ref name=\"hons\" />\n*Runners-up: [[1998\u201399 Scottish Junior Cup|1998\u201399]], [[2006\u201307 Scottish Junior Cup|2006\u201307]]\n\n[[Scottish Junior Football East Region Premier League|SJFA East Region Premier League]]<ref name=\"hons\" />\n*Runners-up: 2006\u201307\n\n===Other Honours===\n*Fife & Tayside (Taycars) Trophy Winners 1997\u201398\n*[[Fife Junior Football League|Fife Junior League]] winners: 1990\u201391, 1991\u201392, 1992\u201393, 1996\u201397, 1998\u201399\n*[[Scottish Junior Football Fife District League]]: 2002\u201303\n*Fife Junior (PSM) Cup: 1982\u201383, 1983\u201384, 1984\u201385, 1986\u201387, 1992\u201393, 2007\u201308, 2008\u201309\n*Cowdenbeath (Interbrew) Cup: 1981\u201382, 1984\u201385, 1985\u201386, 1986\u201387, 1992\u201393, 1999\u201300\n*Laidlaw Shield winners: 1983\u201384, 1984\u201385, 1986\u201387\n*Clark Beckett Cup: 1993\u201394\n*ACA Sports League Cup: 2006\u201307\n*Maloco Associates (Fife) Cup: 2007\u201308, 2008\u201309\n*Rosslyn Trophy Winners : 1991\u201392, 1996\u201397\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://keltyhearts.co.uk/ Official club site]\n* [http