ish volleyball clubs]]\n[[Category:ZAKSA K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale| ]]\n[[Category:ZAKSA K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale seasons| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox volleyball club\n| clubname    = Grupa Azoty<br> ZAKSA K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale\n| short name  = \n| nickname    = \n| image       = ZAKSA_Logo.png\n| fullname    = ZAKSA Sp\u00f3\u0142ka Akcyjna\n| founded     = 1947\n| dissolved   = \n| ground      = [[Azoty Hall]] <br />ul. Mostowa 1 <br />47-223 [[K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale]]\n| capacity    = 3,375\n| chairman    = {{flagicon|POL}} [[Sebastian \u015awiderski]] \n| manager     = {{flagicon|SRB}} [[Nikola Grbi\u0107]]\n| captain     = {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Benjamin Toniutti]]\n| league      = [[PlusLiga]]\n| season      = \n| position    = \n| website     = http://www.zaksa.pl/\n| pattern_la1 = \n| pattern_b1  = _yellowshoulders\n| pattern_ra1 = \n| pattern_s1  = \n| leftarm1    = FFFFFF\n| body1       = FFFFFF\n| rightarm1   = FFFFFF\n| shorts1     = FFFFFF\n| pattern_la2 = \n| pattern_b2  = _yellowshoulders\n| pattern_ra2 = \n| pattern_s2  =\n| leftarm2    = 003153\n| body2       = 003153\n| rightarm2   = 003153\n| shorts2     = 003153\n| current     = \n}}\n'''Grupa Azoty ZAKSA K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale''', previously known as '''Mostostal-Azoty K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale''', is a [[Poland|Polish]] [[volleyball]] team based in [[K\u0119dzierzyn-Ko\u017ale]], playing in [[PlusLiga]]. \n\n==Achievements==\n* [[CEV Champions League]]\n*: [[File:Bronze medal europe.svg|16px]] '''(x1)''' [[2002\u201303 CEV Champions League|2003]]\n* [[CEV Cup]]\n*: [[File:Simple silver cup.svg|16px]] '''(x1)''' [[2010\u201311 Men's CEV Cup|2011]]\n* [[CEV Challenge Cup]]\n*: [[File:Simple bronze cup.svg|16px]] '''(x1)''' 2000\n* [[PlusLiga|Polish Championship]]\n*: [[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|16px]] '''(x8)''' 1998, 2000, [[2000\u201301 PlusLiga|2001]], [[2001\u201302 PlusLiga|2002]], [[2002\u201303 PlusLiga|2003]], [[2015\u201316 PlusLiga|2016]], [[2016\u201317 PlusLiga|2017]